>Description:
When sending a bug report fails, the dialog that reports that failure doesn't allow to scroll the text in the field, because when the mouse-cursor is over the scrollbar, still the "copy this message" popup menu will be displayed.
>How-To-Repeat:
Send a bug report whose submission will fail, try to use the scrollbar in the error dialog that pops up.
